README.md
     5в†’## Usage
     7в†’To start using the library, install it in your project:
     8в†’
     9в†’```bash
    10в†’npm install sonner
    11в†’```
    12в†’
    13в†’Add `<Toaster />` to your app, it will be the place where all your toasts will be rendered.
    14в†’After that you can use `toast()` from anywhere in your app.
    15в†’
    16в†’```jsx
    17в†’import { Toaster, toast } from 'sonner';
    18в†’
    19в†’// ...
    20в†’
    21в†’function App() {
    22в†’  return (
    23в†’    <div>
    24в†’      <Toaster />
    25в†’      <button onClick={() => toast('My first toast')}>Give me a toast</button>
    26в†’    </div>
    27в†’  );
    28в†’}
    29в†’```
    30в†’
    31в†’## Documentation
    33в†’Find the full API reference in the [documentation](https://sonner.emilkowal.ski/getting-started).
